## Quick Reference — What You're Building
```
User types MBL
      ↓
Agent builds URL  (system prompt Step 1)
      ↓
browser_navigate  (Playwright MCP on Railway)
      ↓
browser_snapshot  (returns rendered page text)
      ↓
Agent extracts data  (system prompt Step 3)
      ↓
Returns JSON table
